Chord data as example data for the chord_plot function.

Source: R/chord_data.R
chord_data.Rd

Chord data as example data for the chord_plot function.

Usage

data(chord_data)

Format

Dataframe: include columns (Samples, Set1, Set2, ...), rows (Gene1, Gene2, ...).

References

https://github.com/BioSciTools/BioSciToolsDatasets/tree/main/ChordPlot/

Author

benben-miao

Examples

# 1. Library TOmicsVis package
library(TOmicsVis)

# 2. Load example data
data(chord_data)

# 3. View example data
chord_data
